data.description: Check this out! Charming horse property nestled on a vast 1.5-acre expanse! Inside, you are immediately welcomed by a perfectly-sized living room & a great room that exudes a sense of spaciousness and freedom, creating an environment perfect for both relaxation and entertainment. The wood flooring, which stretches throughout the residence, adds warmth & an organic touch to the interiors. Impeccable kitchen has ample white cabinets, built-in appliances, granite counters, recessed lighting, & an island w/a breakfast bar. The cozy main bedroom showcases an ensuite w/dual sinks & a separate tub. The backyard offers a lot of potential, be it landscaping for aesthetic purposes or practical horse-related facilities. What are you waiting for? Visit right now!
